{"tid":1330530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民陣已申請到維園足球場作為遊行起步點","createTime":"2019-07-18T15:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T16:00:12.000Z","uid":240362,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ba4c1255928b85e9da8467e7ab8d4a1218bafba","tid":1330530,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:07:22.000Z","msg":"【 起點集合地點更新 】民陣今日已進一步申請到維園足球場作為遊行起步點，擴闊更大空間予大家聚集，在此感謝 維多利亞社區協會 的幫忙。香港人，721，下午三時見。<br />\n<br />\n另外亦要通知大家，當日中午有另一團體在港島發起大遊行，視乎速度或者對我們的起步時間稍有影響，我們將盡力安排大家盡快起步，而打算中途加入的市民亦請留意，謝謝。"},{"pid":"2909e0e4ac972e19985f999d5e9b4a507af4bb5f","tid":1330530,"uid":142332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:08:03.000Z","msg":"由簡做起 由自己地區做起 踢走送中人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MUddIkuu2qJnkO6MJtnz7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMUddIkuu2qJnkO6MJtnz7A&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=477c22c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MUddIkuu2qJnkO6MJtnz7A</a><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得 仲有三個月就區選？<br />\n<br />\n其實時間過得好撚快 話咁快就一個半月 跟住又好快咁過<br />\n好快d人又唔記得區選唔投得保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n區選為民主既第一步 自已區自已救！<br />\n<br />\n所以 我係度成立地區文宣 support街站朋友<br />\n提算每區政治度！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n入左group 歡迎就地區議題自由討論<br />\n歡迎任何有心人pm admin入working group負責出圖"},{"pid":"db7f0b7def10df79128d6edc7eb1ef414d9fdd33","tid":1330530,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/67229165_472617676647666_7877051595177852928_n.png?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGDLHePgA-pncGlDNIZaTVwLweBexdcWsNvRN1uBoWH3AXcPtIa-v6-ht59Jhw-kINuRKft90ilNUk_NkWIxMs0s40TJwpxJg8JqkHx8Cc9cg&amp;_nc_oc=AQn6Mo7ZB9N7Y5fn8xepyQ7L1obSfkboBoGn0eaX5wu5U2zegeirRFPoEqjr3GO7GmA&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=987a0421b73